{"tid":1221564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"永別東亞，擁抱滙豐。","createTime":"2019-06-14T08:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T08:44:18.000Z","uid":40184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"16c6831a26d77534102222cc3ff53c4dddd7b940","tid":1221564,"uid":40184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:44:18.000Z","msg":"前幾日的起心肝去左滙豐開左個户口出糧用，<br />\n再將東亞啲錢轉曬美金現鈔放夾萬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱放工再攞埋本簿仔去取消埋個户口！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇得出個teller已經對啲客取消户口見慣不怪，<br />\n連個取消原因都幫我諗埋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我想話取消原因係對中資銀行冇信心咖，<br />\n但見佢咁好人就費事留難佢了。<br />\n滙豐張卡快啲到啦！<br />\n咁到時就可以取消埋個中銀户口喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/31tujjF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F31tujjF.png&h=6d38f9d0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}